---
source: starstream-compiler/src/typecheck/tests.rs
description: "Source:\n\nutxo Counter {\n    storage {\n        let mut multiplier: i64;\n    }\n\n    main fn update(x: i64, y: i64) {\n        let pub w = disclose(x + y);\n        multiplier = w;\n    }\n}\n"
---
T-Utxo: Counter => 
  T-Fn: update => ()
    T-Let: {multiplier: i64, x: i64, y: i64} ⊢ let pub w = disclose(x + y); ⇒ i64
      T-Disclose: {multiplier: i64, x: i64, y: i64} ⊢ disclose(x + y) ⇒ i64
        T-Bin-Add: {multiplier: i64, x: i64, y: i64} ⊢ x + y ⇒ i64
          T-Var: {multiplier: i64, x: i64, y: i64} ⊢ x ⇒ i64
          T-Var: {multiplier: i64, x: i64, y: i64} ⊢ y ⇒ i64
          Unify-Const: i64 ~ i64 => {}
    T-Assign: {multiplier: i64, w: i64, x: i64, y: i64} ⊢ multiplier = w; ⇒ i64
      T-Var: {multiplier: i64, w: i64, x: i64, y: i64} ⊢ w ⇒ i64
      Unify-Const: i64 ~ i64 => {}
